{"tid":596154,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家試過發咩惡夢","createTime":"2018-03-17T10:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T16:11:25.000Z","uid":5348,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"726c82fb7681174d44d496f256c79c805c1e6b16","tid":596154,"uid":5348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:57:12.000Z","msg":"細個間唔中都發埋一個差唔多一樣劇情既惡夢<br />\n<br />\n翻屋企搭lift 永遠都搭唔到自己個層 跟住諗住出lift行翻去自己個層 又行唔到 仲要愈行愈高 行到百幾層樓高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋後面會有d人追自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  通常跑到自己仆街就會嚇醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地試過發咩惡夢"},{"pid":"15a187522bcf878d0e7a09c63e22ff040a334d9b","tid":596154,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:58:53.000Z","msg":"發完唔記得lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a262554f0bfce6597f2247794f7af7ad6b6b9fa","tid":596154,"uid":5348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15a187522bcf878d0e7a09c63e22ff040a334d9b","tid":596154,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:58:53.000Z","msg":"發完唔記得lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:00:40.000Z","msg":"終有d印象深刻既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e6912c6b9df3889088c06b9e65b3766328e196","tid":596154,"uid":5348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>發完唔記得lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>總有d印象深刻既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" clas