g":"1.入lift去到自己果層 行到去個&ldquo;行&rdquo;仔到搵唔到自己屋企對門<br />\n2.行樓梯先發覺唔係自己果層再行返去自己果層<br />\n3.loop 1,2"},{"pid":"57476c770eef6980065f9d7e9bd3eb939dca2a88","tid":596154,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:38:38.000Z","msg":"有次發夢 自己一個望落屋企下面 屋企樓下好多南亞人係到 個樣好惡咁望上黎我地屋企 講曬d我地聽唔明既話 最恐怖係屋企門口有人一直扔野落我地對門到 同埋想搵硬野撞爆我屋企對門<br />\n果時發緊夢完全唔知得罪佢地d野 佢地好似想殺我地咁"},{"pid":"32867709ec961071d75ae54b457639789f56c98e","tid":596154,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:50:37.000Z","msg":"1 發夢槍戰，我學拍戲d人避係架車後面。<br />\n但係子彈射穿架車射中我個身，中左兩發子彈。<br />\n個身好痛，但係又冇流血。<br />\n<br />\n2 發夢去日本旅行係山腳玩雪突然遇到雪崩，即刻帶住條女避難逃走，逃走過程要游水過河又要爬城牆"},{"pid":"b3ec323479d7e6e805afe492e145c8bc132f779d","tid":596154,"uid":77257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:52:09.000Z","msg":"有次發夢瞓緊覺<br />\n半夜3點門鐘響<br />\n我落床去門個防盜眼望下<br />\n見到對面有個赤裸，個身好多污漬既長髮男人，佢踎住望住我<br />\n之後我即刻返入房<br />\n點知一入房就見佢踎咗係屋入面<br />\n嚇到即醒成身汗"},{"pid":"ef5b7c217f6b4d4490e8f37201f95dbc4d3780bc","tid":596154,"uid":5348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a3ebb36652873b9888989a78c0f0ddbb354d9a7","tid":596154,"uid":57506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:34:27.000Z","msg":"1.入lift去到自己果層 行到去個&ldquo;行&rdquo;仔到搵唔到自己屋企對門<br />\n2.行樓梯先發覺唔係自己果層再行返去自己果層<br />\n3.loop 1,2"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:57:35.000Z","msg":"唔知有幾多人發過呢d夢 我都係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a664c3e474ac80b71ae7258673755f67f4f4276","tid":596154,"uid":5348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce2e28bdfe57aa53ec351fc08c5334bad822f561","tid":596154,"uid":133673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:28:57.000Z","msg":"其實我一晚平均發四五個夢算點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"夢中夢中夢中夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8b6a28ad834f1c925575e5e10065d3bd9d08fe","tid":596154,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T12:11:17.000Z","msg":"返工日子瞓過龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e305dd43d642a834a1105efb0761d56354d85e4","tid":596154,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T12:18:18.000Z","msg":"琴晚<br />\n發夢見到gugudan最細2個成員做左我個妹。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/201520_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F201520_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d8da339f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">大妹(康美娜)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/201540_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F201540_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a8ad2579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">二妹(趙慧妍)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後打仗 我同<span style=\"color: gold;\">大妹(康美娜)</span> 成為第一隊戰鬥人員 正準備出戰 點知轉個撚頭過話解散 <br />\n<br />\n變成全國人都要參戰 要用身份證過大閘(好似香港e道咁 ) 咁我地又出戰 我同兩個妹 仲有見到 我阿嫲 原來阿嫲都係一個戰士<br />\n<br />\n但因為我地第一隊戰鬥人員 解散資料未del 出唔到閘 <span style=\"color: gold;\">二妹(趙慧妍)</span>出左閘 見我同大妹(康美娜)入唔到 兩個妹都喊曬口 最後都係分開左 <span style=\"color: gold;\">二妹(趙慧妍)</span> 先去戰場。好撚驚冇左個妹(就<br />\n親人)<br />\n<br />\n我同<span style=\"color: gold;\">大妹(康美娜)</span> 最後係坐香港地鐵返家<br />\n<br />\n轉個撚頭 去撚左場 電音show 見到我fd 之後唔知同佢講咩q野 坐低睇show 點知<span style=\"color: gold;\">zedd</span>(電音Dj) 講我隔離(好撚緊張<br />\n<br />\n我又驚又開心 之後同佢講(英文):好欣賞佢我都有作曲 問佢啲技巧 最後話會去佢黎緊香港個 EDM show 之後光速完show(夢show) 離場<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/201745_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F201745_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d8211628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">ZEDD</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訓醒<br />\n完"},{"pid":"f6206dfe3c847f39ea6a88479ed329f254d1f3cc","tid":596154,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"579482096ad07713db214d133ff55ed0e676f765","tid":596154,"uid":5348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"042038b0736c9ce665a80216da2ceeea0b73f3fc","tid":596154,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28a8c65e35bff9e5c560987aa22e4354b7c76ba3","tid":596154,"uid":165024,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"呢個夢斷斷續續咁發咗幾年。夢入面的我畀個著和服嘅長髮女人綁架，有次趁個女人瞓咗，偷走，點知被佢發現咗。好彩一個身穿民國中山裝嘅男學生踩單車嚟救我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:09:54.000Z","msg":"夢中情人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"醒下啦 假嫁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我的真命天子呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdb1e334e80846a19ee81de8820a839de2c8814","tid":596154,"uid":37374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"709210d80eb72669ea87509c402dbd4cc047b976","tid":596154,"uid":45659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:25:34.000Z","msg":"我都試過好多次發搭life又係搭極都出唔到咁，又去唔到個層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都好恐怖。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T12:30:21.000Z","msg":"我都試過好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過呢排無咩點再發"},{"pid":"5d2939fbaeab075211ebe1d300e23de5bf1770be","tid":596154,"uid":68014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T12:34:10.000Z","msg":"夢就真係唔記得晒，但記得訓醒有淚痕仲眼濕濕<br />\n<br />\n利申男人"},{"pid":"ce6a47db9